General.Name: Cullen Resources Ltd
General.Description: Cullen Resources Limited, together with its subsidiaries, engages in the mineral exploration activities in Western Australia and Finland. It primarily explores for gold, lithium, nickel, copper, iron ore, and platinum group element, as well as base metals. The company was incorporated in 1982 and is based in South Perth, Australia.
